To provide the functionality where admins can define and assign roles to users, we will:

1. Create models to handle roles and user-role assignments.
2. Implement services to define roles and assign roles to users.
3. Develop controllers and routes to manage roles and user-role assignments.
4. Ensure only admins can access the relevant functionalities.

Epic Title: Role-based Access Control

Given the folder structure and user story, we will:
1. Define the `Role` and `UserRole` models.
2. Implement the service to handle operations related to roles and user-role assignments.
3. Create controllers and routes for managing roles.
4. Make sure these operations are only accessible to admins.

